1.0.name: wordpress/mimbolove
1.0.description: Mimbolove is a simple, customizable theme for WordPress with support for custom menu, header image, two column layout, footer sidebar. Sticky post support, and Gallery, Image post formats, featured images are some of the other features supported. Mimbolove is suitable for those who write more on their blog, and also for those who publish photos.
